# Common Issues and Solutions
- Theme not loading styles or scripts: Check asset path helpers and enqueue functions
- ACF fields not appearing: Check field group conditions and location rules
- Blade templates not rendering: Check template name and path conventions
- Custom post types not showing: Check rewrite rules and flush permalinks
- Database queries slow: Add indexes and optimize JOIN operations
- Caching issues: Clear object and transient caches
